thread.title: Lori

author: Lori
title: Lori
text: I purchased several items they all were great quality better then I expected. The price was right, the shipping I thought was high until I received the package, it was a pretty large package so all in all the shipping was very fair. Will continue to purchase from Clear bags. I feel like I just up my game in my online business with the products I purchased. Shipped very fast received it early.
